.SH NAME
Navigator.connection \- Navigator: connection property
.SH SYNOPSIS
The \f[B]\f[CB]connection\f[B]\f[R] read\-only property of the
\f[CR]Navigator\f[R] interface returns a \f[CR]NetworkInformation\f[R]
object containing information about the system\[cq]s connection, such as
the current bandwidth of the user\[cq]s device or whether the connection
is metered.
.PP
This could be used to select high definition content or low definition
content based on the user\[cq]s connection.
.SH VALUE
A \f[CR]NetworkInformation\f[R] object.
